## API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint                        | Description           | Auth     |
|--------|---------------------------------|-----------------------|----------|
| POST   | /api/auth/register              | Register user         | Public   |
| POST   | /api/auth/login                 | Login                 | Public   |
| GET    | /api/vehicles                   | Get vehicles          | Customer |
| POST   | /api/vehicles                   | Add vehicle           | Customer |
| GET    | /api/bookings/slots             | Get available slots   | Auth     |
| POST   | /api/bookings                   | Create booking        | Customer |
| PUT    | /api/bookings/:id/status        | Update status         | Admin/Mechanic |
| POST   | /api/invoices                   | Create invoice        | Admin    |
| GET    | /api/admin/dashboard            | Dashboard stats       | Admin    |
| GET    | /api/admin/queue                | Garage queue          | Admin    |

## Features

- ✅ JWT Authentication with role-based access (Customer/Admin/Mechanic)
- ✅ Vehicle management with smart service recommendations
- ✅ Calendar-based slot booking with double-booking prevention
- ✅ Real-time repair status tracking with timeline
- ✅ Invoice generation with GST calculation and PDF print
- ✅ Email notifications (Nodemailer) + SMS simulation
- ✅ Admin dashboard with charts (Recharts)
- ✅ Mechanic assignment and task management
- ✅ Spare parts inventory with low-stock alerts
- ✅ Garage queue monitoring
- ✅ Pickup & drop service requests
- ✅ Service cost estimator
- ✅ Responsive design with Tailwind CSS
